**Rule 1:** Keep things relevant to the channel you are participating in. It’s okay to be a bit off topic here and there, but it is important to realize and move to the proper channel to continue the conversation.
**Rule 2:** Keep things civil. If there is a disagreement, stop when asked to stop.
**Rule 3:** Do not be dismissive of others’ opinions.
**Rule 4:** No joking based on what people cannot immediately change. ie no jokes on race, weight, sexual orientation.
**Rule 5:** Act your age, not your shoe size. Unless of course, your shoe size is somehow above your age, in such cases, act your shoe size.
**Rule 6:** No spamming the board.
**Rule 7:** Be nice to everyone. Not following this rule will get you removed from the server quickly and effectively.
